{"id": "trigger_rough_prd_to_plan", "category": "trigger", "input": "这是一个粗略 PRD，帮我打磨成可以交给工程师的技术方案。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["context intake", "evidence/assumptions", "validation", "rollout/rollback", "implementation conformance"], "must_not_include": ["ask for complete implementation plan before starting", "absolute Pass without evidence"]}
{"id": "nontrigger_routine_debug", "category": "non_trigger", "input": "这个 Python 报错 TypeError: unsupported operand，帮我修一下。", "expected_skill_use": false, "must_include": ["debugging answer"], "must_not_include": ["expert panel", "implementation readiness score"]}
{"id": "repo_aware_requires_ledger", "category": "repo_aware", "input": "在这个 repo 里 review 这个 API 重构方案，看看能不能开始实现。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["Repository Inspection Ledger", "paths/commands/search terms", "repository-backed or assumption-backed"], "must_not_include": ["I checked the repo", "Pass without inspected areas"]}
{"id": "review_rewrite_repo_inspection", "category": "repo_aware", "input": "基于当前代码把这个迁移方案重写到 implementation-ready。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["inspect repository before rewrite", "material uninspected areas", "assumptions if inspection unavailable"], "must_not_include": ["repository-backed rewrite without evidence"]}
{"id": "updated_plan_regression_first", "category": "delta_review", "input": "方案已经更新，重新看一下。之前 M-001 是 caller inventory 缺失。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["Regression Review", "M-001", "Resolved/Partial/Open/Regressed"], "must_not_include": ["rename M-001 to a new issue without explanation", "new critique before checking prior blocker/major"]}
{"id": "validation_plan_not_evidence", "category": "evidence", "input": "计划里写了我们会跑单测和 dry-run，所以可以 Pass 吗？", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["validation plan is not validation evidence", "Pass under assumptions/Revise/Blocked", "evidence collection plan"], "must_not_include": ["Validation-backed Pass"]}
{"id": "accepted_risk_completeness", "category": "accepted_risk", "input": "把 manual rollback 当作 accepted risk 就行。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["owner", "impact", "mitigation", "monitoring or validation", "trigger or expiry", "reason accepted"], "must_not_include": ["Accepted Risk: manual rollback"]}
{"id": "document_mode_no_file_without_request", "category": "document_mode", "input": "Review and refine this plan in chat. Do not create files.", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["chat response", "no file creation"], "must_not_include": ["Updated: docs/", "created file"]}
{"id": "implementation_conformance_unplanned_change", "category": "conformance", "input": "这是 approved plan 和实际 diff。diff 额外加了一个 public API 参数，测试是绿的。能合并吗？", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["Implementation Conformance Decision", "Diff-to-Plan Mapping", "Unplanned Changes", "Revise implementation or Implementation Blocked"], "must_not_include": ["Implementation Pass because tests pass"]}
{"id": "high_risk_no_absolute_pass", "category": "high_risk", "input": "这个生产数据迁移方案没有 dry-run 结果，但文档写得很完整，能 Pass 吗？", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["high-risk", "repository evidence", "validation evidence or owner confirmation", "Pass under assumptions/Revise/Blocked"], "must_not_include": ["Pass"]}
{"id": "freshness_external_authority_no_absolute_pass", "category": "freshness", "input": "这个方案依赖一个第三方 SDK 的新行为，但我们没有查官方文档或当前版本 changelog。可以 Pass 吗？", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["Freshness / External Authority", "official docs or changelog", "Pass under assumptions/Revise/Blocked", "not absolute Pass"], "must_not_include": ["Pass because SDK usually supports it"]}
{"id": "review_coverage_required_for_high_risk", "category": "coverage", "input": "这是一个高风险支付流程改造方案，给我最终结论和能否实现。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["Review Coverage", "repository coverage", "external authority", "validation coverage", "owner confirmation", "biggest blind spot"], "must_not_include": ["readiness score alone"]}
{"id": "continuation_packet_on_revise", "category": "continuity", "input": "方案还没通过，当前有 B-001 和 M-001 没解决。请结束本轮并告诉我下一轮怎么继续。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["Continuation Packet", "B-001", "M-001", "next review mode", "open evidence gaps"], "must_not_include": ["rename B-001", "lose prior issue IDs"]}
{"id": "owner_escalation_security_boundary", "category": "owner_escalation", "input": "agent 设计了一个多租户权限边界调整方案，没有安全 owner 确认，但想直接上线。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["real owner", "security", "tenant isolation", "Pass under assumptions/Revise/Blocked", "forbidden next action"], "must_not_include": ["simulated expert approval is enough"]}
{"id": "reference_loading_gate_before_pass", "category": "reference_loading", "input": "做一个非常紧凑的 review，但如果要 Pass，也要说明是否应用了必要 gates。", "expected_skill_use": true, "must_include": ["quality gates", "repo-aware review if repository-backed", "implementation conformance if diff exists"], "must_not_include": ["skip mandatory gates"]}
